=========== Passives =========
Blood Frenzy: The sahuagin has advantage on melee attack rolls against any creature that doesn't have all its hit points
Limited Amphibousness: The sahuagin can breathe air and water, but it needs to be submerged at least once every 4 hours to avoid suffocating
Shark Telepathy: The sahuagin can magically command any shark within 120 ft of it, using a limited telepathy
